{"tid":1404730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大肚蔡少芬著斗零踭出活動 工作人員貼身傍實","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T05:49:22.000Z","uid":48905,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d5875a647bb60f29349f5912ec9bdb027602557d","tid":1404730,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"現年45歲﹑第3度懷孕的打工仔蔡少芬（Ada），早前跟老公張晉返重慶探親，昨天Ada在內地出席品牌活動，Ada身穿深色鬆身裙示人，側面看就見她肚凸凸，雖然佗住BB，但Ada仍腳踏斗零踭，看到也覺牙煙，不過有工作人員貼身傍實，並捉住Ada隻手以防萬一，而面帶笑容Ada亦跟市民揮手，只是步履稍為緩慢，全程小心翼翼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AV9MtDH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAV9MtDH.png&h=4f02b421&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b77ee91fc11dcf018aef942c557c85d97d3f55a","tid":1404730,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1PAmZe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1PAmZe.png&h=891e8950&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebf54c0d6e579dd3dd011920dcc4104bbd43342b","tid":1404730,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yr6SpcF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyr6SpcF.gif&h=c4e06b08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7af85715e283246ad44feb54326e893dd0aa48d","tid":1404730,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/baGGhxL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbaGGhxL.png&h=da045461&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}